#. Pj.2.7.16"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms.319"></a>
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pj2:135.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññataro bhikkhu saṃghassa bhisiṃ theyyacitto avahari."
